7
00:01:59,950 --> 00:02:00,640
The Ice Lotus?

8
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:03,950
He consumed half of his Golden Core

9
00:02:04,230 --> 00:02:05,230
to nurture the Reincarnation Tree,

10
