11
00:02:07,400 --> 00:02:08,240
to complete the Golden Core.

12
00:02:09,240 --> 00:02:09,750
Now,

13
00:02:10,680 --> 00:02:11,470
with the Ice Lotus Technique broken,

14
00:02:11,750 --> 00:02:13,190
that half of the Golden Core has shattered as well.

15
00:02:13,920 --> 00:02:15,550
So he has fallen from the Transcendence Stage,

16
00:02:16,230 --> 00:02:17,310
and his spiritual power is now imbalanced.

17
00:02:18,079 --> 00:02:18,970
If we don't find a way

18
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:19,910
to stabilize his spiritual power,

19
00:02:20,630 --> 00:02:21,680
he'll go berserk

20
00:02:21,980 --> 00:02:22,780
and live a life worse than death.

21
00:02:23,870 --> 00:02:25,079
I will find a way to save him.

22
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:26,800
However,

23
00:02:29,310 --> 00:02:30,490
